title: Grateful Dead Live at Starlight Theater on 1984-07-03
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi DR-1) -> Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) -> KORG AudioGate 4 -> Samplitude Professional v11.2.1 -> FLAC 24/96; Edited & Mastered with Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
taper: Robert Bryant patched out of Oade Brothers - from the Gastwirt collection
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Promised Land, Candyman, Cassidy, West L.A. Fadeaway, My Brother Esau, Loser-> Looks Like Rain-> Deal

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Touch Of Gray-> Fire On The Mountain-> Scarlet Begonias-> Don't Need Love-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E: Day Job
